
ID:4
Title: Checking the minimize button.

Priority:
High

Prerequisites:
N/A

Test type:
Positive (+)

Environment:
Windows 10, Chrome  80.0.3987.149

Description:
Test describes the results of checking  the screen minimizing button.

Test scenario:
    1.Open the chat.
    2.Click the minimize button located in the upper right corner.
    3.The chat window is minimized.

The expected results:
    1.The chat is opened.
    2.The minimize button located in the upper right corner is clicked.
    3.The chat window is minimized.
